nodes.descrip: hey @jack0wsky , @karlhorky , @sol-idsnake and @aravind-tc there is nothing wrong with GatsbyJS its how NodeJS handle piping data into closed streams, the error might be caused when the NodeJS event loop didn't clean-up closed TCP connections from the HTTP connection pool and then the NodeJS runtime attempted to use the closed TCP connection.
